def compute_rounded_sqrt_iterations(n):

    x = 2 * 10 ** ((d - 1) // 2) if d % 2 != 0 else 7 * 10 ** ((d - 2) // 2)
    i = 1
    while True:
        new_x = (x + np.ceil(n / x)) // 2
        i += 1
        if new_x == x:
            return i
        x = new_x
